---
title: Panko-Crusted Tilapia with Mango Salsa plus Rice, Sweet Chili-Lime Mayo & Cilantro
description: Inspired by the tropical flavors of the Caribbean, our chefs created a dish for Black History Month that pairs panko-crusted fried tilapia with a vibrant, tangy-sweet mango-cilantro salsa for the perfect balance of sweetness and acidity. Serve with fluffy white rice and chili-lime mayo to complete the meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/678555da29a6fb95e15c1d50-9414f3cb.jpeg
